  (analytic isolated-zeros theorem specialized to a compact rectangle);
- `StripGapToLC` : certificate-count bridge from a geometric strip gap
  to right-local-constancy of the weighted count. -/
theorem concreteS_halfLogPlusHalf_of_numericalExtraction_and_localFiniteZeros
