-- §CCXLII. Concrete zeroDensity model package
-- =====================================================================
-- Replaces the abstract `ActualCloudDensityModelData` in the front door
-- with concrete, named pieces: the explicit smooth tail model built
-- from `zeroDensityRho` (§CCXLI), the finite cloud `pairedFiniteCloudFromZeros`,
-- and an explicit model-equation hypothesis. Threads through to the
