/-- **Concrete smooth tail model for `zeroDensityRho`.** Direct alias
of the `tailModel` field of §CCXLI's `smoothDensityTailModelData_zeroDensityRho`.
Exposed as a named function so the model-equation hypothesis (`hmodel`)
can be written readably in terms of it. -/
noncomputable def zeroDensitySmoothTailModel
    (T : ℝ) (hT_ge : 2 * Real.pi ≤ T) : ℂ → ℂ :=
  (smoothDensityTailModelData_zeroDensityRho T hT_ge).tailModel

/-- 🌟🌟🌟 **PROVED — `ActualCloudDensityModelData` from a
zeroDensity-style cloud + smooth tail model equation.** Specializes
§CCXXXII's `actualCloudDensityModelData_of_smoothTail` to the concrete
`zeroDensityRho` smooth tail constructed in §CCXLI. -/
noncomputable def actualCloudDensityModelData_of_zeroDensityCloudModel
    (us : List ℝ)
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition)
    (hzeros : M.zeros = zeros100ceil)
    (T : ℝ) (hT_ge : 2 * Real.pi ≤ T)
    (hmodel : ∀ z : ℂ,
        M.model z =
          pairedFiniteCloudFromZeros us z +
            zeroDensitySmoothTailModel T hT_ge z) :
    ActualCloudDensityModelData :=
  actualCloudDensityModelData_of_smoothTail us M hzeros
    (smoothDensityTailModelData_zeroDensityRho T hT_ge) hmodel

/-- 🌟🌟🌟🌟 **PROVED — `XiActualTailDecompositionData` from concrete
zeroDensity pieces.** Combines:

* `us`, `M`, `hzeros`, `Tsmooth`, `hTsmooth_ge`, `hmodel` —
  concrete model side via `actualCloudDensityModelData_of_zeroDensityCloudModel`;
* `error`, `P : XiLogDerivativeDecompositionPieces M error` —
  three-piece xi decomposition (§CCXXXIV);
* `herror` — residual Im match (xi-specific).

Discharges `hdecomp` via §CCXXXIV automatically. -/
noncomputable def XiActualTailDecompositionData.ofZeroDensityPieces
    (Dzero : Phase1IBP.OrderedFluctuationMeasureData) (T0 : ℝ)
    (hT0_pos : 0 < T0) (hT0_le_10 : T0 ≤ 10)
    (hTuring :
      ∀ {z : ℂ} {T u : ℝ},
        10 ≤ T → T ≤ 140 → 0 < z.im →
        2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) ≤ T →
        T ≤ u →
        |Phase1IBP.finiteFluctuationPrimitive Dzero T0 u|
          ≤ (slabCD T).1 * Real.log u + (slabCD T).2)
    (us : List ℝ)
    (M : CloudDensityTailModelDecomposition)
    (hzeros : M.zeros = zeros100ceil)
    (Tsmooth : ℝ) (hTsmooth_ge : 2 * Real.pi ≤ Tsmooth)
    (hmodel : ∀ z : ℂ,
        M.model z =
          pairedFiniteCloudFromZeros us z +
            zeroDensitySmoothTailModel Tsmooth hTsmooth_ge z)
    (error : ℂ → ℂ)
    (P : XiLogDerivativeDecompositionPieces M error)
    (herror :
      ∀ {z : ℂ} {T : ℝ},
        10 ≤ T → T ≤ 140 → 0 < z.im →
        2 * (1 + |z.re| + z.im) ≤ T →
        (error z).im =
          (trueKernelAdaptiveTail Dzero T0 hT0_pos hT0_le_10 hTuring T z).im) :
    XiActualTailDecompositionData Dzero T0 hT0_pos hT0_le_10 hTuring :=
  XiActualTailDecompositionData.ofPieces
    Dzero T0 hT0_pos hT0_le_10 hTuring
    (actualCloudDensityModelData_of_zeroDensityCloudModel
      us M hzeros Tsmooth hTsmooth_ge hmodel)
    error P herror

/-- 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟 **CLEAN FINAL FRONT DOOR (concrete model).**
End-to-end conditional capstone using:

* `hTuring` — Turing/Backlund log envelope (parallel agent);
* concrete model: `us`, `M`, `hzeros`, `Tsmooth ≥ 2π`, `hmodel`
