```
hTuring + hHighLog              (parallel agent)
+ Hcanon_tailLimit              (mid residual Tendsto)
+ Hhigh_tailLimit               (high residual Tendsto)
+ Hlow_explicit                 (xi: residual ≤ closed-form first-zero bound)
+ Hlow_arith                    (model-side: pure arithmetic on the box)
⟹ XiPullbackAntiHerglotzTarget
```

The `Hlow_arith` input is `LowExplicitArithmeticBound` — no complex
