/-- 📦 **`FirstZeroAdjustedSBound Dzero T0 γ D`** — direct abs bound:
`|finiteFluctuationPrimitive Dzero T0 u| ≤ D` on `[11, γ]`. This is
the shape actually consumed by the IBP closure. -/
structure FirstZeroAdjustedSBound
